content:
You may already have an Amazon Connect instance or want to manage your own Amazon Web Services account. Service Cloud Voice with Partner Telephony from Amazon Connect lets you integrate your own Amazon Connect instance with Service Cloud Voice.

REQUIRED EDITIONS
Available in: Lightning Experience, Enterprise and Unlimited Editions, Sales Cloud, Service Cloud, Government Cloud as an add-on license.

These tasks apply to this telephony model:

Turn on Service Cloud Voice with Partner Telephony from Amazon Connect
Enable Voice for your org.
Configure AWS Identity and Access Management (IAM) Role for Voice

Create a Partner Amazon Contact Center
With Service Cloud Voice with Partner Telephony from Amazon Connect, you turn on Service Cloud Voice and then integrate it with an Amazon Connect instance.
title: Setting Up Service Cloud Voice with Partner Telephony from Amazon Connect
